### Files Modified

- `src/Sharpy.Compiler/Semantic/ImportResolver.cs` - Fixed function parameter population
- `src/Sharpy.Compiler/Semantic/TypeChecker.cs` - Added member access function call handling

The semantic analysis for nested module access (`lib.math.add(5, 3)`) now works correctly! The remaining code generation issue in integration tests is a separate pre-existing problem that's outside the scope of this task.
